reviewText: this product lives up to it's promise of giving you a real workout and makes you feel like you have done something

I have the Power Sculpt, Cardio Max, Boot Camp, Last Chance Workout and Weight Loss Yoga DVDs but was very disappointed in these first DVDs from the Biggest Loser line. I haven't even looked at one of them because the first was so disappointing. The "high intensity" 20 minute cardio was lame and was definitely not 20 minutes long. I guess this was their first attempt at workout videos and they got better with the later ones. unfortunately, I started with the later DVDs, so these look very amateur.
